<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp;&nbsp; 新春送温暖，关怀聚人心。在2024年新春佳节来临之际，我校组织开展了寒假春节送温暖慰问活动。为同学们带来温暖和鼓励。<br style="box-sizing: border-box;"/>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">家庭走访慰问活动温暖人心</strong><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"/>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 2月5日，校党委书记、督导专员江延湖，执行校长范红铭，学工处副处长王晶，经管学院党总支书记蔡平一行前往高安市黄沙岗镇岗头黄村慰问困难学生，了解学生的家庭、经济收入、生活和寒假安排，并送上慰问品和诚挚的新年祝福，让家庭经济困难学生和家长在寒冬中感受到来自学校的真诚关爱和浓浓暖意。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-02-07%2011%3A50%3A3666.gif?Expires=2022637837&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=29Ah0xtIfOjug8eJCxh%2Bc4EzzpE%3D" alt="" width="800" height="525" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"/>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 走访期间，校领导与同学们亲切交流，详细了解同学们的家庭情况、主要困难，认真听取家长对学校工作意见与建议，鼓励同学们磨练意志，珍惜时光、刻苦学习、练就本领，将暂时的苦难当做前进的动力，以优异的成绩回报父母、学校和社会，在不懈奋斗中实现青春梦想。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-02-07%2012%3A20%3A5777.jpg?Expires=2022639657&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=oc9F0NRQyQ2LrVC%2B9rWNfLGuILo%3D" alt="" width="800" height="600" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"/>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 受慰问同学及家人非常感动，在表示寒假期间、在自己家中，也感受到学校老师的温暖和关怀，虽然目前家庭条件不太好，但正在朝着好的方向发展，自己和家人对未来生活充满了信心和期待。<br style="box-sizing: border-box;"/><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; “暖心促就业”走访慰问鼓舞干劲</strong><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"/>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 为积极发挥资助育人与就业育人合力作用，关心2024届学生就业情况，假期，学校组织开展了就业行动计划，开展了寒假“暖心帮扶促就业”专项系列活动。<br style="box-sizing: border-box;"/>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 各学院院长书记带队学工办人员，深入到毕业生家庭中，全面了解学生家庭实际情况，对其在就业创业过程中遇到的困难及原因、学生就业意向等进行详细摸底。同时，还向学生讲解国家、地方和学校各项就业政策，并结合毕业生个人信息、求职意愿等精准推荐用人单位和岗位信息，分析当前就业形势和趋势，鼓励学生树立信心，拓宽视野，积极应对，主动出击。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-02-07%2011%3A36%3A0933.jpg?Expires=2022636969&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=T21lRlGwnVkZN%2Fpf7M73LKNU9zU%3D" alt="" width="800" height="600" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-02-07%2011%3A36%3A5544.jpg?Expires=2022637015&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=%2BaYZRQNty7435M1Vd032LkhQgE0%3D" alt="" width="800" height="603" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-02-07%2011%3A31%3A1922.png?Expires=2022636679&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=bbj%2FOvNrgWtg31ehKfirLNIcg6Y%3D" alt="" width="800" height="544" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-02-07%2011%3A33%3A3655.png?Expires=2022636816&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=cZ%2BIcIWYG0Dn2LDsWLUxyQxvot0%3D" alt="" width="800" height="527" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"/>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">返乡受助学生齐力宣传政策</strong><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"/>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;此外，学校抓住寒假学生返乡这一契机，引导和组织受助学生回家乡、回母校宣传学生资助政策，并结合自己在国家资助政策的帮助下安心学习、健康成长的亲身经历，帮助学弟学妹和他们的家长解除后顾之忧。</p><p><br/></p>